title: Name of Department and Title of Minister) Order 2020 (S.I. No. 408 of 2020)),
heading: 2. The 1st day of February 2021 is appointed to be the establishment day
text_raw:
2. The 1st day of February 2021 is appointed to be the establishment day 
for the purposes of the Housing (Regulation of Approved Housing Bodies) Act 
2019 (No. 47 of 2019). 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

28 January, 2021. 

DARRAGH O’BRIEN, 

Minister for Housing, Local Government and Heritage. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 2nd February, 2021.
